 \frac{u(x)}{1-u(x)}=\frac{W_A}{W_a}\cdot\frac{x}{1-x}, 
 \frac{p(t)}{1-p(t)}=\frac{u^{\circ t}(p(0))}{1-u^{\circ t}(p(0))}=\left(\frac{W_A}{W_a}\right)^t\cdot\frac{p(0)}{1-p(0)}, 
